title: You Are A Child Of Promise | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: You Are A Child Of Promise | Victoria Osteen
description:
When negative feelings come, you have to remind yourself that God knows you. He sees you, and He cares for you. With God on your side, you can do anything but fail!

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
